===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|knowleche||lang=enm}}, from ''[[knowen]]'' "to recognize, know" from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|cnawan|cnāwan||lang=ang|to know}} + {{term|-leche|lang=enm}} a suffix derived from Old English {{term|-læcan|-lǣcan|lang=ang}} verbal suffix denoting activity, from {{term|lac|lāc}} a verbal noun suffix, cf. {{term|wedlock|lang=en}}

